#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:55
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"&i18n-kapplication; is an editor for &kaddressbook; themes based on <ulink "
"url=\"https://github.com/steveire/grantlee\">Grantlee</ulink>."
msgstr ""
"&i18n-कप्लिकेशन; &kaddressbook; <ulink url=\"https://github.com/steveire/"
"grantlee\">अनुदानं</ulink> इत्यस्य आधारेण विषयाः ।"

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:59
#, no-c-format
msgid "Using &i18n-kapplication;"
msgstr "&i18n-kapplication इत्यस्य उपयोगेन;"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:60
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"This editor is used to create themes for your contacts in &kaddressbook;. "
"More Information you find in the <ulink url=\"http://www.grantlee.org/apidox/"
"\">Grantlee</ulink> documentation."
msgstr ""
"एतत् सम्पादकं &kaddressbook; इत्यत्र भवतः सम्पर्कस्य विषयवस्तुनिर्माणार्थं उपयुज्यते । "
"अधिकानि सूचनानि भवन्तः <ulink url=\"http://www.grantlee.org/apidox/"
"\">Grantlee</ulink> दस्तावेजे प्राप्नुवन्ति ।"

